name: LaTeX Periodic Report Professional
version: 1.1.0
author: nguyenpanda
email: hatuongnguyen0107@gmail.com
description: >
  Professional Beamer template for research progress reports.
  Features modern custom fonts (Work Sans, Bernoru, JetBrains Mono),
  complex examples (TiKZ, Algorithms, Math, Listings),
  and a robust automated build system using LuaLaTeX and latexmk.
languages:
- latex
- tex
- latexmk
- make
license: MIT
url: https://nguyenpanda.com
tags:
- latex
- latexmk
- lualatex
- beamer
- presentation
- research
- hcmut
- professional
ignore:
- .git/
- .vscode/
- .idea/
- .DS_Store
- build/
- pdf/
- '*.aux'
- '*.log'
- '*.nav'
- '*.out'
- '*.snm'
- '*.toc'
- '*.vrb'
- '*.fls'
- '*.fdb_latexmk'
- '*.synctex.gz'
hooks:
- echo 'LaTeX Periodic Report Template cloned!'
